<br>
@QM - No thanks, I just finished reading the game and have little interest in doing it again.  If you want to know which ones weren't answered you'll have to find them yourself.<br>
<br>
@Antihero - Gameplay seems more or less null, though I agree with whoever is was that said that he's only likely to be scum if his partner turns out to be one of the more inactive players.  It does bear mentioning that I find the sudden shift that he undergoes when he suddenly decides to stop stonewalling the town a little strange.

Something more about QM: He is trying to stay out of the spotlight and avoids getting into quarrels with the other players. <br>
